{"tid":2083670,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"民政處突封場 打壓抗爭展","createTime":"2020-06-29T02:06:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-29T02:19:47.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"30f68befc1b690e89e020f417359f5689b112c8a","tid":2083670,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T02:06:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200629/WMFMWDHOJTBCAFPPFJK7I2GOSQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200629%2FWMFMWDHOJTBCAFPPFJK7I2GOSQ%2F&d=wLbnxcWodPR608ZqId7G8apJ2kzo9njAZIZZFH2Kh%2FI%3D&h=e0bc29a3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200629%2FWMFMWDHOJTBCAFPPFJK7I2GOSQ%2F&h=8629476b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200629/WMFMWDHOJTBCAFPPFJK7I2GOSQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n民政處突封場 打壓抗爭展<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Rw65GwdgopPeYwrOkAuV27RH0Rw=/640x438/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/THJYCJ2BCR6NPKNUR7ILXWI6IA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FRw65GwdgopPeYwrOkAuV27RH0Rw%3D%2F640x438%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FTHJYCJ2BCR6NPKNUR7ILXWI6IA.jpg&h=049b4f6c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n龔振祺（中）昨與數位藝術家嘗試進入油塘社區會堂，惜大門已上鎖。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】為了在「深藍重鎮」油塘區反映抗爭運動的真相，與假新聞抗衡，油塘東區議員龔振祺原定昨日聯同十位藝術家在油塘社區會堂舉行《第一年的故事》抗爭藝術展覽，惟借用場所申請在兩日前突遭民政事務處拒絕批出場地。龔振祺昨嘗試如常到會堂領取場地，但大門被鎖上無法內進。主辦單位正嘗試另外借用場地，期望重新舉辦展覽。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：跟蹤13日 四神秘人監視黎宅<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3月初獲批 擬追討損失<br />\n<br />\n龔振祺指1月初申請場地，3月初獲批。雖活動牽涉社會事件但立場中立，講座亦有邀請不同立場的社區人士參與討論。展覽本身不會有任何前設，街坊可以從活動中得出不同結論。龔原本打算按原定計劃進社區會堂，但發現大門已被鎖上。昨早大約上午9點45分，有三名軍裝警員<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n龔批評觀塘民政處粗暴打壓，顯示民政處與民為敵，製造白色恐怖，觀塘<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n但「香城教育電視」會繼續與香港人同行抗爭。龔亦藉此呼籲港人不要<br />\n。。。。<br />\n開始十分支持抗爭，但通過對話後仍能說之以理。"},{"pid":"03c8f0c35437fef3f11ac475817e77eee567939b","tid":2083670,"uid":114487,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T02:06:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9HE0Php.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9HE0Php.jpg&h=c5e5f272&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cf95167dc578b619a0b5de57d99660a21e07ed1d","tid":2083670,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T02:07:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc317d4b74abd77215bf9e8f58d0cca0567d56f6","tid":2083670,"uid":78411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T02:12:19.000Z","msg":"71見"},{"pid":"113cd9b78723ca122d61d5878dabc3652064d301","tid":2083670,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc317d4b74abd77215bf9e8f58d0cca0567d56f6","tid":2083670,"uid":78411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T02:12:19.000Z","msg":"71見"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T02:19:43.000Z","msg":"71見"},{"pid":"442f87ce16d60b7496c44f77838b4ac648fd552e","tid":2083670,"uid":10881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T02:19:47.000Z","msg":"push"}]}